                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout>
                           <p>Columns: 1;
                                                  ruled lines: 26 59;
                                                  written lines: 26 59; Uniform layout. Visible hard-point ruling. Pricking is visible in quire xlv. Initial words written in larger characters. Hebrew foliation from folio 8. Erasures (e.g., folios 78r, 179v, 187v, 331v, 380r, 436r). </p>
                        </layout>
